                <div class="section-media-wall--list_description_origin_text">
                  After the last set of software updates and a reboot of the datacenter and Yarbo, everything worked.
                  Strong signal and success in mapping and clearing fresh snow from my driveway. I have lots of trees in
                  a suburban environment with lots of dwellings nearby so my location was not a textbook locating for
                  Yarbo. Tech support was great, the fit and finish of the unit was amazing but was looking at making a
